#!/usr/bin/env bash

notify-send -t 30000 --icon="/usr/share/icons/Papirus/16x16/actions/dialog-error.svg" "If you edit a .conkyrc file, you will need to 
copy it from your home folder, and paste it 
into its folder located in...

~/.config/conky/

Otherwise, your changes won't be available 
from the Conky Chooser in the future.

The name of the conky is at the top of each
.conkyrc file, and that is also the name of 
its folder."